\displaystyle a_n = \frac{n}{\log n}
n \ge 3
\displaystyle \frac{1}{n^2} \sum_{i=1}^n a_i \sim \frac{1}{n^2} \int_3^n \frac{x}{\log x} dx
\displaystyle \frac{1}{n^2} \int_3^n \frac{x}{\log x} dx \leq \frac{n}{n^2} \int_3^n \frac{1}{\log x} dx = O\left(\frac{1}{\log n}\right) \rightarrow 0
